  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK275">
<l>paṟṟaṟṟē meṉpār paṭiṟṟoḻukka meṟṟeṟṟeṉ</l>
<l>ṟētam palavun tarum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The false conduct of those who say they have renounced all desire will one day bring them sorrows that will make them cry out, "Oh! what have we done, what have we done."</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
